title: Didn’t expect overwhelming turnout at Bihar rallies: Ajay Devgn
text: Didn’t expect overwhelming turnout at Bihar rallies: Ajay Devgn Wednesday, 14 October 2015 (15 seconds ago) After missing a chance to address a rally in Bihar due to an "overwhelming turnout", Ajay Devgn feels the organisers were not prepared and urged better arrangements in future.
